---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    I'm a builder and problem solver who thrives at the intersection of AI and practical impact. With a background in civil engineering and minors in computer science and data analytics, I’ve applied machine learning, computer vision, and reinforcement learning to domains ranging from smart mobility to healthcare and retail analytics. I care deeply about user-centric design, measurable impact, and deploying real-world solutions that work — not just prototypes. Currently pursuing a Master’s in Business Analytics at NUS.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container flex flex-col mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="M.Sc Business Analytics"
      subtitle="Aug 2025 to Aug 2026 at National University of Singapore, Singapore"
    >
      Recipient of the NUS Engineering Scholarship.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="B.Eng Civil Engineering (Highest Distinction)"
      subtitle="Aug 2022 to May 2025 at National University of Singapore, Singapore"
      isLast={true} 
    >
      GPA: 4.67 / 5.00 | Dean’s List AY23/24 Semester 1 | NUS Engineering Scholar<br/>
      Specialisation: Digitalisation of Urban Infrastructure<br/>
      Minors in Computer Science and Data Analytics<br/>
      IAHR-Singapore Hydraulics Medal
        
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container flex flex-col mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Scientist Intern at Tictag"
      subtitle="Jun 2025 to Aug 2025 at Tictag, Singapore"
    >
      Designed and implemented scalable video analytics pipelines using RT-DETR and ViTPose for in-store customer interaction detection. Built production-ready ETL workflows for pose classification and ROI event tracking. Delivered business insights from CCTV footage using segmentation and depth models.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Undergraduate Teaching Assistant for CS2040"
      subtitle="Aug 2024 to May 2025 at NUS School of Computing, Singapore"
    >
      Conducted weekly tutorials on data structures and algorithms in Java for 30 students. Guided lab sessions and graded assignments.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Climate Models Analytics Intern"
      subtitle="May 2024 to Aug 2024 at DSTA, Singapore"
      isLast={true} 
    >
      Built a robust pipeline with Selenium and APIs to automate weather data retrieval. Enhanced rainfall analysis using super-resolution models (SRGAN, RDN). Deployed a Llama-based offline chatbot to support domain experts in meteorology.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li><a href="#" target="_blank">Google Data Analytics Certificate</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" target="_blank">DeepLearning.AI Generative AI with LLMs</a></li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>PyTorch</li>
    <li>TensorFlow</li>
    <li>Scikit-learn</li>
    <li>XGBoost</li>
    <li>OpenCV</li>
    <li>LangChain</li>
    <li>FastAPI</li>
    <li>React</li>
    <li>TypeScript</li>
    <li>SQL</li>
    <li>PostgreSQL</li>
    <li>Docker</li>
    <li>Git</li>
    <li>Jupyter</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
